desc_content.paragraph: Line set for associating lines and style parameters
Specify a logical combination of selection conditions on feature edge types

list_item.paragraph: OR Logical OR, Select feature edges satisfying at least one of edge type conditions.
AND Logical AND, Select feature edges satisfying all edge type conditions.

desc_content.paragraph: Specify either inclusion or exclusion of feature edges selected by edge types

list_item.paragraph: INCLUSIVE Inclusive, Select feature edges satisfying the given edge type conditions.
EXCLUSIVE Exclusive, Select feature edges not satisfying the given edge type conditions.

desc_content.paragraph: Exclude border edges
Exclude contours
Exclude crease edges
Exclude edge marks
Exclude external contours
Exclude edges at material boundaries
Exclude ridges and valleys
Exclude silhouette edges
Exclude suggestive contours
Specify a feature edge selection condition based on face marks

list_item.paragraph: ONE One Face, Select a feature edge if either of its adjacent faces is marked.
BOTH Both Faces, Select a feature edge if both of its adjacent faces are marked.

desc_content.paragraph: Specify either inclusion or exclusion of feature edges selected by face marks

list_item.paragraph: INCLUSIVE Inclusive, Select feature edges satisfying the given face mark conditions.
EXCLUSIVE Exclusive, Select feature edges not satisfying the given face mark conditions.

desc_content.paragraph: A collection of objects based on which feature edges are selected
Specify either inclusion or exclusion of feature edges belonging to a collection of objects

list_item.paragraph: INCLUSIVE Inclusive, Select feature edges belonging to some object in the group.
EXCLUSIVE Exclusive, Select feature edges not belonging to any object in the group.

Determine how to use visibility for feature edge selection

list_item.paragraph: VISIBLE Visible, Select visible feature edges.
HIDDEN Hidden, Select hidden feature edges.
RANGE QI Range, Select feature edges within a range of quantitative invisibility (QI) values.
